Key Match Events: Paolo Banchero scored 34 points in his return to action
Pre-Game Insights: Coach Jamahl Mosley said his team “didn’t have the energy needed” to win against Minnesota
Post-Match Reflections: There might not have been anything better to give Orlando a much-needed boost of energy vs. Milwaukee other than the return of Paolo Banchero
Miscellaneous Highlights: Paolo Banchero made his way back to the court after a 34-game absence due to a torn right abdominal muscle
Others: The Magic fell to the Timberwolves by 15 points on Thursday night
